Along with the idea that mannaburn is balanced because wizards can't win any other way. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ugrayrage.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Grayrage</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(7/11/02 7:57:48 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm27.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=65.topic&index=37>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> well</span><hr size=1> With the addition of SOL, I feel much better in pvp playing a wizzie.   I do not think we lack for anything and are a competitive class.  We can be beaten and we can win...which is how it should be.  <br>
<br>
